    <item>
      <title>Re: trade skills</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Trade&amp;message.id=12380#M12380</link>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;To defray the expense, farm fine steel weapons from mobs - these can be converted to small bricks and pieces of HQ ore, which can in turn be combined to make large bricks of HQ ore. Plenty of zones come to mind - Mistmoore, SolA and Lower Guk are 3 that pop immediately to mind (for levels 20-40) - plenty of other places to find fine steel as well. While this will reduce the expense per combine, it will increase the time per combine.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You could also look to find fine steel weapons in the Baz, but that could become an expensive propistion&lt;/p&gt;</description>
