      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Best thing is to use the EQtraders trivial list, and just scan down until you find something you want to attempt.  Some recipes are more resonable than others, some cultural isn't bad to do either.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/recipe_quicklist.php?rsa=Smithing&amp;menustr=080100900000"&gt;http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/recipe_quicklist.php?rsa=Smithing&amp;amp;menustr=080100900000&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For example - &lt;span class="headers"&gt;&lt;font size="3"&gt;Embroidering Needle (trivial 122) - &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1190"&gt;&lt;font size="2" color="#800000"&gt;celestial essence&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1120"&gt;&lt;font size="2" color="#800000"&gt;metal bits&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1738"&gt;&lt;font size="2" color="#800000"&gt;needle mold&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1001"&gt;&lt;font size="2" color="#800000"&gt;water flask&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="headers"&gt;Also, if you are doing ornate combines, do the bracers which only take 1 high quality metal ring. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="headers"&gt;&lt;span class="headers"&gt;&lt;font size="3"&gt;Small Ornate Gold Bracelet (trivial 132) - &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1087"&gt;&lt;font size="2" color="#800000"&gt;gold bar&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=2106"&gt;&lt;font size="2" color="#a66868"&gt;high quality metal rings&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=2038"&gt;&lt;font size="2" color="#800000"&gt;small chainmail bracelet pattern&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=3086"&gt;&lt;font size="2" color="#800000"&gt;smithy hammer&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1001"&gt;&lt;font size="2" color="#800000"&gt;water flask&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="time_text"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Zacatac_BB on &lt;span class="date_text"&gt;04-04-2006&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="time_text"&gt;09:18 AM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
